[
  {
    "text": "Welcome to the Apple TV Distribution Program Overview.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "This program is for TV providers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are interested in partnering with Apple ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "to distribute Apple TVs to customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "as an over-the-top set top box replacement.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's get started.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video we'll go through the Zero Sign-On user experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how to support it with the authentication context, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "VideoSubscriberAccount framework, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the set top box APIs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Apple TV Distribution Program ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "enables Apple TV to become the center ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your customers' content consumption experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "During Apple TV setup, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "your TV provider brand is promoted ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the Apple Zero Sign-On user experience is enabled.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "Customers are presented ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a welcome screen to your service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "informing them of the automatically ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "authenticated account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the TV provider app to be installed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "This allows customers to have a seamless experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "with your service so they can watch video ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "right out of the box.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, and one more thing, all of these features work ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "even if the customer doesn't have an iTunes account.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "So that's Zero Sign-On.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, the authentication context.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "The technology at the center of all of these features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "is your authentication context.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is what allows customers to sign-in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your TV provider service at the OS level.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "This system-level authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "is then leveraged to provide seamless authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=79"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "and any other TV provider-supported apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "on device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "The authentication context is a web service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "hosted on your server that is downloaded to device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "and executed at run time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is built using JavaScript and XML, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a single authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "runs on both iOS and tvOS.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "With authentication at the system level, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "customers only have to sign in once with Single Sign-On ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "or not at all with Zero Sign-On.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's authentication context.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next is the VideoSubscriberAccount ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=111"
  },
  {
    "text": "framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "This framework is what allows your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "and any other TV provider-supported apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "to communicate with your authentication context ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "to request its app-level authentication.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "When integrating with ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "the VideoSubscriberAccount framework, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's important to remember that you're dealing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "with authentication at two different levels.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "You will need to request authentication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the system for your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "From that point forward, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "your app's authentication state ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "needs to mirror the system authentication state.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "This requires special attention ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "for all the different UI and UX flows coming into your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once implemented, you will deliver your apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the Apple Media Products video team via TestFlight ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a final QA sign-off.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is required before submitting the app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "to App Store review for approval and release.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's VideoSubscriberAccount framework.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "Last are the set top box APIs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "they are what enable Apple TV ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "to know which TV provider to feature.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "They also allow TV providers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "without an in-home auto-authentication solution ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "to automatically authenticate customers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple TVs distributed by you will feature your TV service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "to customers in the setup process.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this same screen, customers are informed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=184"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the auto-authenticated account and app to be installed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=186"
  },
  {
    "text": "The set top box APIs are a server-to-server communication ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "used to assign to and remove profiles from devices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "The APIs will only work with Apple TVs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "purchased from Apple for distribution by you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "So that's the set top box APIs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "Through Zero Sign-On, the authentication context, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "the VideoSubscriberAccount framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "and set top box APIs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=211"
  },
  {
    "text": "the Apple TV Distribution Program ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "enables Apple TV to become the center ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=215"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your customers' TV experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "In summary, the Apple TV Distribution Program ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "highlights your TV provider brand, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "it promotes your applications to the customer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "and eliminates the sign-in process for your customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "enabling Apple Zero Sign-On.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Apple TV Distribution Program ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Zero Sign-On are a win-win ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "because your customers get a customized, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "streamlined experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you get more visible promotion ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Apple TV experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-504/?time=245"
  }
]